216	#CreateAccountText	default	<font style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.2em;font-family:optima">  \r\n<div style="text-align:left">Authors need to register and log in to request peer-reviews and recommendations for their preprints</div>   \r\n<div style="text-align:left">New recommenders and reviewers need to register and log in to act as recommenders and reviewers</div>    \r\n<div style="text-align:left">After registration, you will receive an e-mail for validation. This may take several hours. If you do not receive any mail for validation, please contact us at <a href="mailto:?to=%(contact)s">%(contact)s</a></div>  \r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style="text-align:left">Complete the following fields in order to create your profile on %(longname)s.</div>   \r\n&nbsp;\r\n</font>
